OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FGradually
OL,6,Fturning cloudier through the evening
OL,7,Fwith patchy rain arriving later and
OL,8,Fcontinuing overnight, potential for
OL,9,Fsome heavier busrts over hills.
OL,10,FTurning increasingly blustery through
OL,11,Fthe early hours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA dull and blustery day, with
OL,14,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, which could
OL,15,Fbe heavy at times. Gradually improving
OL,16,Ffrom the north with bright or sunny
OL,17,Fspells possible later. Feeling milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
